'''Prisht fruit''' was a sweet [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]] that could be used to make [[Prisht-fruit salad|salads]]. [[Barlok/Legends|Barlok]] was known for growing fine prisht and it was the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] most prized produce.<ref name="Outbound" />

